title: Breathe (Taylor's Version)
description:
Taylor Swift really wanted to work with Colbie Caillat on the Fearless album so she brought her back for the re-recording of Breathe.. and there is a reason why Colbie is more audible on this version! If you don't know what this song is really about, the answer may surprise you. It hits some of us differently.
What do you think of this song? What did we miss? Hit us up with all of your thoughts!
